rows.label: qev055105_MSG0001
rows.name:
A Definian's camouflage is extremely difficult to spot
unless you are paying close attention.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055105_MSG0002
rows.name:
Please be careful as you continue to gather information.
Our friend's life is in your hands.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055105_MSG0003
rows.name:
Sun'celeg is a weapons-development specialist.
If he is kidnapped, it is bad for everyone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055105_MSG0004
rows.name:
For if so, there is a 67.5 percent likelihood that the
Ganglion intend to brainwash him into crafting
weapons for them once more.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055105_MSG0005
rows.name:
Taken positively, that means that barring exceptional
circumstances, the chances of him being killed are quite
low. Regardless, please see him back to us quickly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055105_MSG0006
rows.name:
Even if he has been brainwashed, it will be a simple
matter to remove any such programming with our
technology.[ST:wait ]
